Class CSSFunctionCallPropertyValue

    ISourceLocation, ICSSNode, ICSSPropertyValue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CSSURLAndFormatPropertyValue

    public class CSSFunctionCallPropertyValue
extends CSSPropertyValue
    Base class for CSS function call property values.

    For example: Embed("bg.png").
